videos.headline: Warriors pull away in second half for win over 76ers
videos.description: The Warriors step up in the second half as they grab a 127-104 road win over the 76ers.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Warriors pull away in second half for win over 76ers) 2024/02/08 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Curry shocked when and-1 3-pointer is overturned
videos.description: Steph Curry thinks he has the 3-pointer plus the foul, but he can't believe it when it's overturned to an offensive foul after review.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Curry shocked when and-1 3-pointer is overturned) 2024/02/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Beverley makes sweet crossover into a layup
videos.description: Patrick Beverley attacks the basket with a nice crossover before putting in the bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Beverley makes sweet crossover into a layup) 2024/02/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kuminga forces a 76ers timeout with game-tying score
videos.description: Jonathan Kuminga gets the layup for Golden State's 10th straight point, forcing Philadelphia to take a timeout.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Kuminga forces a 76ers timeout with game-tying score) 2024/02/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Moody splashes 3 after offensive rebound
videos.description: Warriors attack the glass with the ball ending up with Moses Moody for a 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Moody splashes 3 after offensive rebound) 2024/02/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kuminga flies in for the dunk
